title: Rules
description: Here are the rules for ThumbTac's discord server!

fields.name: Rule #1
fields.value: No discrimination of any kind such as racism or sexism

fields.name: Rule #2
fields.value: Keep the chat english only when possible

fields.name: Rule #3
fields.value: Don't swear excessively or at others

fields.name: Rule #4
fields.value: No spamming or loud noises in chat or vc

fields.name: Rule #6
fields.value: Never give out any personal information of anyone

footer.text: If you stick around, we'll assume you've read the rules. Staff can punish people at any time for any reason as writing every single rule is impossible.
